      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 03:19:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>人工智能和折扣助力需求，智能手机市场增长 6%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/smartphone-market-grows-6-as-ai-and-discounts-help-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[独立研究显示，随着整体智能手机市场加速增长，苹果公司 iPhone 的出货量在 6 月份季度趋于稳定。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-15/smartphone-market-grows-6-as-ai-and-discounts-help-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 15 Jul 2024 02:30:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为何现场音乐成为媒体交易最热门的市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-07-14/why-live-music-became-the-hottest-market-for-media-deals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着联邦政府起诉音乐会巨头 Live Nation，私募股权公司正在斥资数十亿美元收购现场音乐资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-07-14/why-live-music-became-the-hottest-market-for-media-deals</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:25:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>TikTok 预计到 2030 年韩国文化支出将翻一番，达到 1430 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/tiktok-sees-k-culture-market-doubling-to-143-billion-by-2030</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据 TikTok 和分析公司 Kantar 发布的最新研究，到 2030 年，全球在韩国文化产品的支出预计将增加近一倍，达到 1430 亿美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-14/tiktok-sees-k-culture-market-doubling-to-143-billion-by-2030</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 14 Jul 2024 22:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
